data.description: Best of both worlds! Excellent Macon location with Monroe County taxes. Beautiful 4 bedroom, 3 bath home with wide-open floor plan. Hardi Board and brick exterior with a landscaped backyard that offers a large covered deck, a second lower-level deck,  fire pit area, fence,  and privacy. Hardwood floors extend throughout the main living area; all bedrooms are carpeted. Charming kitchen was updated in 2020 and includes stainless steel appliances, gas range & oven, quartz countertops, and solid wood cabinets.   Breakfast room and formal dining room give plenty of space for family meals and entertaining. The large primary bedroom has trey ceilings and is on the main floor.  There are two additional bedrooms downstairs with a shared bath. French doors were added to the office to offer privacy for the days when you need to work from home. Large windows allow tons of natural light in all of the downstairs and MBR. Upstairs offers a generous teen-suite and a bonus room with plenty of closet space. The roof and upstairs A/C unit are both new and were replaced in the fall of 2023. This 2,638 square foot home is full of charm and upgrades. The house backs up to a wooded green zone, and the backyard feels private.    Providence subdivision has parks, walking trails, lighted sidewalks, tennis courts, and a pool with clubhouse area.
